Package: formstools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for working with ODK XLSForms
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person(given = "Ernest", 
                  family = "Guevarra", 
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4887-4415"), 
                  email = "guevarra@ecohealthalliance.org", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Set of utility functions for use by EcoHealth Alliance researchers
    in working with Open Data Kit XLSForms. These functions are aimed at aiding
    users in the data cleaning and data validation process using information
    found in the ODK XLSForms.
